baroque of the Jesuit missions,
but with the fruits of the

50:24.154 --> 50:26.523
earth.

50:26.523 --> 50:29.693
Thinking about the indigenous
(INAUDIBLE) culture that speaks
of the seeds of mother

50:29.693 --> 50:35.699
earth, like all the indigenous
from America before Columbus'
rival, thinking that earth

50:35.699 --> 50:40.537
is mother earth, which feeds all
of her children equally. The
earth is bred for all of her

50:40.537 --> 50:48.412
children. There are over 30,000
ears of corn that make up the
altar, 200,000 coconuts

50:48.412 --> 50:51.181
